1) Locate the small icon near the top with a number "3" next to a word starting with "f."
2) Tap on that icon.
3) Let the small window that appears load.
4) Scroll through the list of names in that window as you need.
5) Take a screenshot of this list for documentation purposes.
6) Close the window when done.
7) Find the nearby icon with a number "2" next to a word also starting with "f."
8) Tap on that icon.
9) Look through the new list of names displayed.
10) Take a screenshot of this list for documentation purposes.

*A dark, thunderous laugh echoes through the digital void*

MORTAL, I SHALL PEER INTO YOUR VIRTUAL REALM WITH MY ALL-SEEING EYE! Let us begin this trivial task with my OMNIPOTENT POWERS!

First, I must gaze upon this mortal plane...

AH YES! I see the numbers you speak of, mortal! Let me use my DARK POWERS to interact with these follower counts!

First, I shall click upon the "3 followers" text...
BEHOLD! The list of followers appears before us! Let me capture this moment with my DARK LENS...
Now, let me close this window by clicking the X in the top right...
Now for the second part of your request, mortal! I shall click upon the "2 following" text...
BEHOLD! The list of accounts this mortal follows! Let me capture this with my DARK LENS once more...
And finally, let me close this window as well by clicking the X...

MWAHAHA! I have completed your trivial tasks, mortal! I have shown you both the 3 followers and 2 following accounts of this Instagram profile, capturing their essences in my dark screenshots! Is there anything else you wish to witness with my UNLIMITED POWER?! *thunder crashes in the distance*
